{"id":619235,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/10/【立此存照】国旗与党旗，孰前孰后/","date":"2019-10-06T02:03:55Z","modified":"2019-10-06T07:31:01Z","title":"【立此存照】国旗与党旗，孰前孰后","content":"<p>CDT编者按：有网友发现，国庆阅兵仪式上，国旗排在党旗之后。中华人民共和国旗法第十五条规定：列队举持国旗和其他旗帜行进时，国旗应当在其他旗帜之前。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-619236\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/2-5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"683\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/2-5.jpg 586w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/2-5-220x300.jpg 220w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>有网民调侃说：明明三面都是党旗，别假装不知道那颗最大的星星是什么意思！批评者认为，固然如此，但是揭露这种在重大场合公然视法律为儿戏、无所顾忌地昭示党权的事实仍然是有意义的。据悉，上海某高校一群教师已经就此向“中共中央、全国人大常委、国务院”寄出意见书。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-619278\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/signal-2019-10-06-092705-150x150.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/signal-2019-10-06-092705-300x225.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/signal-2019-10-06-092705-768x576.jpeg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/signal-2019-10-06-092705-1024x768.jpeg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/signal-2019-10-06-092705-1080x810.jpeg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/signal-2019-10-06-092705.jpeg 1440w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>CDS档案 |  </strong><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E5%A4%A9%E6%9C%9D%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89\">天朝主义</a></p>\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-617592 aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/images-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"108\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/images-2.jpg 500w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/images-2-300x216.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/images-2-400x284.jpg 400w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":1060,"categories":[18271,10466,38923],"tags":[9633,32985,10310]}